# Frequency-Words raw lists — too large for the repo (3-5MB each × 9 langs).
# Pre-stemmed JSONs (`resources/data/frequency-stems-*.json`) are checked in
# as the runtime artifact. To rebuild from scratch:
#   1. Download `<lang>_50k.txt` from github.com/hermitdave/FrequencyWords
#   2. Save as `resources/data/_raw_<lang>_50k.txt`
#   3. Run `php artisan linkwise:build-frequency-stems <lang>`
/resources/data/_raw_*_50k.txt
